      "message": "does this work? FWIU it should fail on any non-auth flags.\n\nsee how CIPD does this\n\nhttps://cs.chromium.org/chromium/infra/go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/cipd/client/cli/main.go?q\u003dcmdInspect\u0026sq\u003dpackage:chromium\u0026l\u003d2039\u0026rcl\u003de18d39eb76c9c7b4c0709c11bda0b2c06483d515\n\n\nhttps://cs.chromium.org/chromium/infra/go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/cipd/client/cli/main.go?sq\u003dpackage:chromium\u0026q\u003dregisterBaseFlags+file:%5Einfra/go/src/go%5C.chromium%5C.org/luci/cipd/client/+package:%5Echromium$\u0026l\u003d132",
      "revId": "f4c3c6c30f24e8c89cd38f6ca6712769a23b2fde",
